How are you doing?

&gt;悪くない
眠い
Not bad.
I&#039;m sleepy.

Akechi
ハハ、君はいつでも自然体なんだね。
Haha.  Relaxed as always, I see.

Akechi
…最近、取材が多くて。どう答えるべきかなって、悩んでたんだけど…
...I&#039;ve been getting interviewed a lot lately, so I&#039;ve been wondering how to answer such questions...

Akechi
無理に飾る必要はないよね。君と話すと、色々気付かされるよ。
I see now that there&#039;s no need to be so roundabout with my responses.  Talking with you helps me realize many things.

Akechi
もし迷惑じゃなければまた声を掛けてもいいかな？
If it isn&#039;t too much trouble, may I speak with you again sometime?

#on way to school

Student1
…ねえ、先輩が言ってたんだけど吉祥寺に変な人があるんだって。
...Hey, I heard from one of my upperclassmen, but apparently there&#039;s some kind of weirdo in Kichijoji.

Student1
見た目とか…明らかにヤバイ感じらしいよ。アンタ、地元でしょ？大丈夫？
Even at a glance, you can supposedly tell right away that he&#039;s bad news.  You live there, don&#039;t you?  Are you okay?

Student2
