Now, what would the police think if they heard my recording?

M
警察に直に見張られるのはまずい。
It&#039;d be bad if we&#039;re put under police surveillance.

M
オマエの身だってどうなるか知れたモンじゃないぜ！？
There&#039;s no telling what&#039;ll happen to you, too!

Makoto
君が白状してくれたら、ここだけの話にしてもいい…
If you confess the truth, I don&#039;t mind just leaving this between the two of us...

Makoto
話してくれるよね？
You&#039;ll tell me, won&#039;t you?

黙秘する
考えさせてくれ
&gt;……
I have a right to be silent.
Let me think about it.
......

Makoto
それ、認めているのと同じね。
That&#039;s the same as admitting to it, you know.

#main character gets phone call

Makoto
どうぞ？
Go ahead.

R
おー、今どこ？便所？いつもんとこで、怪盗団の会議な！
