Let&#039;s continue our talk after school tomorrow.  On the roof.

Makoto
「引き受けてくれる」って前提でね。
Assuming you accept my offer, that is.

R
メンドくせーことになったな…
This is turnin&#039; into a real pain...

#Phantom Thieves discussing this in different very public area

Y
…うかつなんだよ。自覚が無さ過ぎるんじゃないのか？
...You were careless.  I don&#039;t think you truly understood how high the stakes were.

Y
竜司。
Anything to say, Ryuji?

R
なんで俺だけなんだよ？杏だって録音されたろうが！
